text: Paul Emile Lamey was a bobsledder from USA. Lamey competed at the 1968 Winter Olympics and the 1972 Winter Olympics. He was born on 24 December 1938 and died on 15 December 2020.Paul Lamey == References == Category:1938 births Category:2020 deaths Category:American bobsledders Category:Olympians for the United States Category:Sportspeople from New Hampshire Category:People from Manchester, New Hampshire
